imdb.plot outline: The young filmmaker Christopher Engel, is working on the sequel to his biography from 2013. But because he has so much out-cut material, he decides to use is to make a small web-series with 12 episodes. To help him, he then gets his girlfriend to help him with the things that he can't film himself, and then a film friend as well - the youtuber "it's me Milo" who films things in public. It all turns out to be dramatic, as his girlfriends son is having a few problems.
